                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-7 芥菜子 文類-小說 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12169.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(5)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12169.htm">聖誕歌 (CHRISTMAS CAROL) [ SÈNG-TÀN KOA (CHRISTMAS CAROL) ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">聖誕歌 (CHRISTMAS CAROL)
   英國有一个&ecirc;大小說家名叫Dickens（力堅斯；按：狄更斯）1812-1870。伊有寫一篇&ecirc;小說叫做聖誕歌，就是將救主誕做背景來寫出人&ecirc;反悔；不止心適，koh再有thang做咱&ecirc;教示。
 第一齣
毛利&Ecirc;陰魂
   毛利已經過身。故事對chia起點。論伊&ecirc;死，無一點-&aacute; thang僥疑&ecirc;所在。牧師、役場&ecirc;書記發落葬式&ecirc;人，以及Kian-līn攏有tǹg印佇伊埋葬&ecirc;證明書。Kian-līn &ecirc;名佇...<a href="artical-12169.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/49f52bc0ae51d.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/49f52bc0ae51d.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-7 芥菜子 文類-詩 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12173.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(1)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12173.htm">正手KAP倒手 [ CHIÀN-CHHIÚ KAP TÒ-CHHIÚ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">正手KAP倒手
   倒手呵咾正手講：
  兩個相倚來&ecirc;時；
你是比我重倍g&acirc;u，
　雖b&oacute;ng你我是雙生。
 
山水景緻你會為，
請安批信做你來；
獨獨我袂做半項。
  Kap你比並毋應該。
 
正手謙卑應伊講：
  猶久一項我袂leh！
小妹、小弟我袂抱
　毋值你抱&ecirc;好勢。
 
養飼天國&ecirc;細囝，
　就是最高&ecirc;藝術；
你io好勢&ecirc;因端，
  恁厝khah倚佇心肝。
陳清忠譯...<a href="artical-12173.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baac8f3238a6.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baac8f3238a6.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-詩 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12200.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(1)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12200.htm">祈禱無停 [ KÎ-TÓ BÔ-THÊNG ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">「祈禱無停」
「著祈禱無soah」。帖撒羅尼迦（1）5:17.E.R.W Edna. R. worrell.
（五線譜）
1. 祈禱無停！上帝近倚；祈禱無停！伊欲聽我；上帝應允，逐項穩當；祈禱無停！伊欲應咱。
2.祈禱無停！你所欠用；祈禱無停！伊欲贊成；你所要求，上帝歡喜；祈禱無停！伊欲予你。
3.祈禱無停！犯罪&ecirc;時；祈禱無停！用好贏--伊；耶穌原本，也捌受試；祈禱無停！伊欲牽你。
4.祈禱無停！傷悲&ecirc;時。祈禱無停！伊th&aacute;u放你；艱苦袂會瞞過上帝；祈禱無停！伊創好勢。
5.祈禱無停！信仰khah深；祈禱無停！也著專心；深信消滅所有煩惱；祈禱...<a href="artical-12200.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baac98c74651.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baac98c74651.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12203.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(3)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12203.htm">論死人KOH活 [ LŪN SÍ-LÂNG KOH-OAH2 ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">論死人KOH活
 
  耶穌予死人koh活，佇福音書中有記3擺：
1.      予管會堂&ecirc;人G&acirc;i-l&oacute;͘ &ecirc;查某囝koh活。馬太9：
2.     佇拿因予守寡婦人人&ecirc;囝koh活。路加7：
3.     予拉撒路koh活。約翰11：
　　G&acirc;i-l&oacute;͘ &ecirc;查某囝死了後無偌久，耶穌予伊koh活。
　　守寡婦人人&ecirc;囝死，經過一問日（按：應為一兩日），teh欲扛去埋葬，佇路中耶穌予伊koh活。
　　拉撒路已經死4日久，身屍已經發臭味，耶穌佇墓前叫一聲，隨時koh活對墓裡...<a href="artical-12203.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baac96f9e403.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baac96f9e403.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12205.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(2)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12205.htm">袂得赦ê罪 [ BOĒ TIT SIÀ Ê CHOĒ ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">袂得赦Ê罪

「見若講話攻擊人子&ecirc;，欲赦免伊；獨獨見若講話攻擊聖神&ecirc;，不論今世來世無欲赦免伊。」馬太12章32節。這節所講是teh指啥物款&ecirc;罪，也著怎樣來解說？咱大家若患著這款永死永滅&ecirc;罪過，萬事盡休，的確會得thang閃避絕望kap悲感。所以這句咱袂免得著斟酌來研究，靜靜來深想；因為是真要緊&ecirc;問題。咱有信對佇反悔kap信仰會得著罪赦，也有信或是佇今世&aacute;是無論佇來世有這款永袂赦&ecirc;罪－咱真驚－彼个罪就是謗瀆聖神&ecirc;罪。今仔日佇咱&ecirc;中間有濟濟&ecirc;基督徒，信in若使領受洗禮就會得...<a href="artical-12205.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="white" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                                          <a href="../album/artical/full/4baac85ba653b.jpg" target="src"><img src="../album/artical/thumb/4baac85ba653b.jpg" border="0" /></a>
                                      </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </div>
            <div></div>
                      	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1925-10 芥菜子 文類-散文 作者-陳清忠/Tân Chheng-tiong ]</span>
          	  <a href="artical-src12211.htm"><img src="../images/icon_photo.gif" border="0" align="absmiddle" />&nbsp;<span class="be13b">(4)</span></a>          	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-12211.htm">湯匙Ê時代 [ THNG-SÎ Ê SÎ-TĀI ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">湯匙&Ecirc;時代
　　佇正月時為著食siuⁿ濟會害嘴齒&ecirc;物，致到嘴齒疼。父母teh欲chhōa in &ecirc;囝兒去找齒科醫&ecirc;時的確袂免得無想，也奇怪講：遐个無文明&ecirc;野蠻人，怎樣袂予嘴齒疼來苦楚in。野蠻&ecirc;人無倚靠刀仔&aacute;是別項物，in會食真碇&ecirc;肉－這實在是為難&ecirc;事－。人講按呢反轉予in &ecirc;嘴齒不時勇健。刀仔以及別款&ecirc;器具，&aacute;是料理術，強強teh欲予人變做無嘴齒&ecirc;動物。真濟款&ecirc;嘴齒病，野蠻&ecirc;人kap in攏毋相識；獨獨文明&...<a href="artical-12211.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="background:white; margin:0; padding:0">
          <td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width="5" height="25" border="0"></td>
        </tr>
                <tr bgcolor="#fffff9" onmouseover="this.className='trl'" onmouseout="this.className='trn'">
          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px; width:140px; float:left;">
              <table width="100%" height="100" border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="outline_be">
